5|$|In {{the evening}} of the third day, the U.S. {{launches}} a full-scale assault on Al-Asad's presidential palace, aware of the SAS warning about the possible <b>nuclear</b> <b>device.</b> As U.S. Navy SEALs invade the palace, the Marines engage Al-Asad's ground forces. The assault, however, ends in catastrophe when the <b>nuclear</b> <b>device</b> suddenly detonates, wiping out most of the city along with everyone in it.|$|E
